                <note rend="inline" type="source">740.00119 Control (Rumania)/3–2045:
                    Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in the Soviet Union</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Harriman</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Moscow</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1945-03-20T22:00:00+03:00"
                            >March 20, 1945—10 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/> [Received March 21—4:05 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>829. A letter has been addressed to Molotov, in accordance with Department’s 605,
                    March 15, 11 p.m., stating our view that co-belligerent status should not be
                    granted to Rumania at this time and that no decision on this matter should be
                    made except after consultation. Coming after receipt of the categoric rebuff by
                    the Soviet Government for our proposal for general tripartite consultation on
                    Rumania, <pb facs="0531" n="519" xml:id="pg_519"/> I doubt that our views on the
                    question of co-belligerency will carry much weight with the Soviet Government.
                    There is a possibility that our representations may even encourage the Russians
                    to proceed independently to recognize Rumania as a co-belligerent in order to
                    demonstrate the independence of their policy.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Harriman</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
